        "subject": "LU-2641 lov: use new O_LOV_DELAY_CREATE value",
        "message": "LU-2641 lov: use new O_LOV_DELAY_CREATE value\n\nCommit 12ed2e36 (v2.6.35) allocated the 0100000000 flag for\nFMODE_NONOTIFY.\n\nThis changes the flag to the next available one, but if we're using\nunofficial flags, we should probably be exporting it via procfs\nsomehow and reading it at runtime.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: If7dce14fb15fa3ab31235f328f150dfb7605333f\n"
